主要翻译
 
atmospheric adj (relating to the air)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 大气的 dà qì de TC Traditional Chinese 大氣的  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 空气的 dà qì de，kōng qì de 
 -- Air traffic control grounded all of the planes due to poor atmospheric conditions.
 
atmospheric adj (evocative)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 有气氛的 yǒu qì fēn de TC Traditional Chinese 有氣氛的  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 有情调的 yǒu qì fēn de，yǒu qíng diào de 
 -- The streets of London are atmospheric when they are shrouded in fog.

复合形式： 
 
atmospheric pressure n (air pressure)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 大气压力 dà qì yā lì TC Traditional Chinese 大氣壓力  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 气压 dà qì yā lì，qì yā TC Traditional Chinese 氣壓 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 常压 dà qì yā lì，cháng yā 
 -- I have trouble breathing when the atmospheric pressure drops.

